snippet.title: Alien Legacy gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Alien Legacy, Dos PC game produced by Ybarra Productions in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/alien-legacy/42/
Exploring a new planet and setting up a colony in this sci-fi adventure.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
